<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About BMCC UsedBooks Store</title>
    <link href="/styles.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="main">
      <%- include('partials/navigation'); %>
      <div id="content" class="content-panel">
        <div class="hh1">About the program</div>
        <p class="size">
          BMCC UsedBooks Store is a student-led initiative that keeps course
          materials in circulation and out of landfills. We verify every ISBN,
          log each transaction, and host weekly swap events so you can buy or
          sell textbooks without leaving campus.
        </p>
        <div class="team-grid">
          <div class="team-card">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544723795-3fb6469f5b39?auto=format&fit=crop&w=300&q=80"
              alt="Maya Patel"
            />
            <h3>Maya Patel</h3>
            <p class="span_cont">Program Coordinator</p>
            <p>
              Maya schedules donation drives and keeps our listing guidelines up
              to date so every buyer knows exactly what they're getting.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="team-card">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544005313-94ddf0286df2?auto=format&fit=crop&w=300&q=80"
              alt="Luis Romero"
            />
            <h3>Luis Romero</h3>
            <p class="span_cont">Quality Lead</p>
            <p>
              Luis inspects donated books, checks for missing pages, and labels
              every copy with an honest condition rating.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="team-card">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521572163474-6864f9cf17ab?auto=format&fit=crop&w=300&q=80"
              alt="Serena Wong"
            />
            <h3>Serena Wong</h3>
            <p class="span_cont">Logistics & Pickup</p>
            <p>
              Serena coordinates lockers and on-campus pickup appointments so
              transactions are quick, safe, and accessible.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>
          All proceeds fund emergency textbook grants for BMCC students. Thanks
          for helping us keep the cycle going.
        </p>
      </div>
      <%- include('partials/footer'); %>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
